#   c "I was just as confused as you were, you have to believe that."
    c "Estaba tan confundido como tú, tienes que creerlo."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:274
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_e428e768:

#   c "Falling in love with your own sister, I mean, the taboo surrounding our love is reason alone to be confused."
    c "Enamorarte de tu propia hermana, quiero decir, el tabú que rodea nuestro amor es razón suficiente para estar confundido."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:275
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_f35e62e1:

#   c "So I panicked and not telling you or Céline became easier than confronting the situation."
    c "Así que me entró el pánico y no decírtelo ni a ti ni a Céline fue más fácil que afrontar la situación."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:277
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_6df3e4f4:

#   l "Céline isn't aware either?"
    l "¿Céline tampoco lo sabe?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:279
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_93506557:

#   c "She knows there are others, but that's all."
    c "Sabe que hay otros, pero eso es todo."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:281
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_bdd0bff8:

#   c "No, she isn't."
    c "No, no lo está."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:283
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_ee5be636:

#   l "Do you...{w} love her?"
    l "¿Tú...{w} ¿Quererla?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:287
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_8a29e1eb:

#   c "Yes, I do."
    c "Sí, me gusta."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:289
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_b1fe9428:

#   l "Thank you for your honesty.{w} Finally."
    l "Gracias por su honestidad.{w} Finalmente."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:290
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_6e61fa05:

#   c "However, my love for you is something more special."
    c "Sin embargo, mi amor por ti es algo más especial."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:291
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_d82fb6c3:

#   c "You complete me, Lilly, like a sister and a lover."
    c "Me completas, Lilly, como una hermana y una amante."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:292
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_bc99d2a2:

#   c "That's something Céline, or any other girl like her will never be able to do. "
    c "Eso es algo que Céline, o cualquier otra chica como ella, nunca podrá hacer. "

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:294
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_bb7488c9:

#   "Lilly stared at me, her lip trembling."
    "Lilly me miró fijamente, con el labio tembloroso."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:295
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_265e408a:

#   l "I really want to believe you."
    l "Realmente quiero creerte."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:297
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_5f3042ba:

#   l "But are you saying I have to accept that you share a bed with Céline as well?"
    l "¿Pero estás diciendo que tengo que aceptar que compartas la cama con Céline también?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:301
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_2ec66c7d:

#   c "No, because I'm going to break up with her."
    c "No, porque voy a romper con ella."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:302
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_186a948f:

#   c "You're the only one for me."
    c "Eres el único para mí."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:304
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_4669c29c:

#   l "I haven't even said if I still want to be with you."
    l "Ni siquiera he dicho si todavía quiero estar contigo."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:305
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_d098608f:

#   c "I don't care, it's the right choice and only fair to the both of you."
    c "No me importa, es la decisión correcta y justa para los dos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:307
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_86b157a7:

#   "I could tell there was some relief in Lilly's eyes."
    "Pude notar cierto alivio en los ojos de Lilly."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:308
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_36d5bdd4:

#   "Whether it would be enough I didn't know, but it was all I could do."
    "No sabía si sería suficiente, pero era todo lo que podía hacer."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:309
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_5353ac80:

#   c "I'll leave you be for now, but I hope you can find it in your heart to forgive me."
    c "Te dejaré en paz por ahora, pero espero que puedas encontrar en tu corazón la forma de perdonarme."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:310
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_c9e6a8a8:

#   "I left Lilly in a state of confusion, hoping it would all turn out for the best."
    "Dejé a Lilly en un estado de confusión, esperando que todo saliera bien."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:312
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_ff60203c:

#   c "I can't change who I am and I love you both."
    c "No puedo cambiar lo que soy y os quiero a los dos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:313
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_5380c9f8:

#   c "I know it's an enormous thing to ask you to accept that I will continue to love both of you, but I'll ask it nonetheless."
    c "Sé que es algo enorme pedirte que aceptes que seguiré queriéndoos a los dos, pero te lo pediré de todos modos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:314
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_2b109f94:

#   c "Whatever answer you'll give me, I'll love and respect you forever."
    c "Sea cual sea la respuesta que me des, te querré y respetaré siempre."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:315
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_fe3610a5:

#   "Doubt filled Lilly's eyes as she contemplated my request."
    "La duda llenó los ojos de Lilly mientras contemplaba mi petición."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:317
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_5f414d17:

#   l "I...{w} I can't...{w} I don't..."
    l "Yo...{w} No puedo...{w} Yo no..."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:319
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_00758326:

#   l "Could you please leave me alone for a while?"
    l "¿Podrías dejarme en paz un rato?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:320
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_4e8c7062:

#   c "Of course."
    c "Por supuesto."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:321
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_2fc60e3f:

#   "I left Lilly in a state of utter confusion, hoping it would all turn out for the best."
    "Dejé a Lilly en un estado de confusión absoluta, con la esperanza de que todo saliera bien."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:324
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_68f24faf:

#   c "I know it isn't fair how this got sprung onto you and I don't want to hurt you anymore than I already did."
    c "Sé que no es justo que te hayan echado esto encima y no quiero hacerte más daño del que ya te he hecho."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:326
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_53772e88:

#   l "What are you trying to tell me, [p_name]?"
    l "¿Qué intentas decirme, [p_name]?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:327
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_08dea339:

#   c "What I'm saying is that Céline isn't the only woman I'm involved with."
    c "Lo que estoy diciendo es que Céline no es la única mujer con la que estoy involucrado."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:328
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_7bd22a1b:

#   c "Monogamy is something I have never believed in."
    c "La monogamia es algo en lo que nunca he creído."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:329
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_dfdcbe18:

#   c "I love women, simple as that."
    c "Me encantan las mujeres, así de simple."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:331
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_ea309f5a:

#   l "Stop, just stop!"
    l "¡Para, para!"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:332
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_d2efe326:

#   l "Leave me alone, [p_name]!"
    l "¡Déjame en paz, [p_name]!"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:333
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_568cc3cd:

#   "I left a visibly confused Lilly, wondering if telling her everything had actually broken our relationship beyond repair."
    "Dejé a una Lilly visiblemente confusa, preguntándome si contárselo todo había roto realmente nuestra relación sin remedio."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:336
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_b98a6224:

#   c "I thought I did, but I've come to realize that I don't."
    c "Creía que sí, pero me he dado cuenta de que no."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:338
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_a8a8d3ed:

#   l "Why haven't you broken up with her then?"
    l "¿Por qué no has roto con ella entonces?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:339
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_255ecca1:

#   c "I will."
    c "Lo haré."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:340
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_90e2f638:

#   c "I hope you can find it in your heart to forgive me, Lilly, I really do."
    c "Espero que puedas encontrar en tu corazón la forma de perdonarme, Lilly, de verdad."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:343
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_31a69a69:

#   l "Hey."
    l "Hola."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:345
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_a1493bde:

#   "Lilly turned around and walked inside her quarters, leaving the door open."
    "Lilly se dio la vuelta y entró en sus aposentos, dejando la puerta abierta."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:346
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_0a444492:

#   "I followed her in."
    "La seguí dentro."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:347
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_f87c9e50:

#   c "Lilly, what's the matter?"
    c "Lilly, ¿qué pasa?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:349
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_7a05d1c2:

#   "Suddenly, she faced me and threw herself in my arms."
    "De repente, se encaró conmigo y se arrojó a mis brazos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:350
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_c91115cc:

#   l "Oh, [p_name_short], I thought I'd lost you!"
    l "¡Oh, [p_name_short], pensé que te había perdido!"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:351
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_a4848853:

#   l "Things have been so awful around here."
    l "Las cosas han sido tan horribles por aquí."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:352
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_420be9b7:

#   l "You gone, Nadya revealing her story..."
    l "Te has ido, Nadya revelando su historia..."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:354
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_a74432d3:

#   l "I just couldn't deal."
    l "Simplemente no podía lidiar."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:355
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_281fc046:

#   l "So I've just been avoiding everyone."
    l "Así que he estado evitando a todo el mundo."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:356
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_7e9f3281:

#   c "Eva told me."
    c "Eva me lo dijo."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:357
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_68654725:

#   c "She also told me you've stayed at my side."
    c "También me dijo que has permanecido a mi lado."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:358
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_84b8fe13:

#   l "Of course I did, I was so afraid I'd lost you."
    l "Claro que sí, tenía tanto miedo de perderte."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:360
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_331a216d:

#   "In response, we exchanged a passionate kiss."
    "En respuesta, intercambiamos un apasionado beso."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:362
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_e0e48401:

#   l "What are we going to do now, [p_name_short]?"
    l "¿Qué vamos a hacer ahora, [p_name_short]?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:363
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_bb00a52c:

#   c "What do you mean?"
    c "¿A qué te refieres?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:364
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_066a50a2:

#   c "Kissing seemed like a great idea."
    c "Besarse parecía una gran idea."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:366
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_d879b47c:

#   l "Not that, you big lump."
    l "Eso no, grandullón."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:367
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_c63d7046:

#   l "I mean about everything that Nadya told."
    l "Me refiero a todo lo que contó Nadya."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:368
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_1054b8c9:

#   c "I'm not sure there's anything to do?"
    c "¿No sé si hay algo que hacer?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:370
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_6e156863:

#   l "You're not angry?"
    l "¿No estás enfadado?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:371
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_0743fd8c:

#   c "Yes, very."
    c "Sí, mucho."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:372
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_15b96add:

#   c "But I'm not angry at Nadya."
    c "Pero no estoy enfadado con Nadya."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:373
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_4b681ffd:

#   c "She must have gone through hell back then."
    c "Debió de pasar por un infierno entonces."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:374
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_26977e52:

#   c "Of course she could have told us earlier, but all things considered, I'm just glad that she did eventually."
    c "Por supuesto, podría habérnoslo dicho antes, pero en general, me alegro de que al final lo haya hecho."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:376
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_3c54f4dd:

#   l "Oh..."
    l "Oh..."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:377
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_bad49f67:

#   l "I was so furious at first."
    l "Al principio estaba furiosa."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:378
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_9248f29b:

#   l "But once I thought things over I feel much the same way you do."
    l "Pero una vez que he reflexionado, pienso lo mismo que tú."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:380
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_0661a5f8:

#   l "Just confronting Aunt Nadya again...{w} no...{w} Mom..."
    l "Sólo enfrentarse a la tía Nadya de nuevo ... {w} no ... {w} Mamá ..."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:381
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_b693412a:

#   l "It's all so weird."
    l "Es todo tan raro."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:382
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_a12465a4:

#   l "I mean, Dad and Nadya together..."
    l "Quiero decir, papá y Nadya juntos..."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:383
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_d2a9f9e5:

#   c "Well, considering our relationship, we're not the ones to judge."
    c "Bueno, teniendo en cuenta nuestra relación, no somos quién para juzgar."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:385
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_4863e00c:

#   l "I know..."
    l "Lo sé..."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:387
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_d4b37849:

#   l "Nadya surely thinks I hate her."
    l "Nadya seguramente piensa que la odio."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:388
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_6dfd1676:

#   c "I'm sure she understands."
    c "Seguro que lo entiende."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:389
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_878b7af5:

#   c "The only thing she's ever wanted was for us to be together."
    c "Lo único que siempre ha querido es que estemos juntos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:390
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_1261fdf5:

#   c "So I was thinking of having a family dinner together."
    c "Así que estaba pensando en tener una cena familiar juntos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:391
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_24ecef7f:

#   l "Dinner?"
    l "¿A cenar?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:392
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_7ab91b14:

#   c "Yeah, with just the five of us."
    c "Sí, sólo nosotros cinco."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:394
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_c6c955e3:

#   l "Okay..."
    l "Bueno..."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:395
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_07128a69:

#   c "You don't sound convinced?"
    c "¿No parece convencido?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:397
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_d563aaeb:

#   l "It's just...{w} what will she think of me?"
    l "Es que...{w} ¿qué pensará de mí?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:398
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_78353f5b:

#   c "She'll understand, I'm sure of it."
    c "Lo entenderá, estoy seguro."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:400
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_0231d669:

#   l "Okay, if you say so."
    l "Vale, si tú lo dices."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:401
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_da1dca2b:

#   c "So I can count on you for dinner?"
    c "¿Entonces puedo contar contigo para cenar?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:402
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_c32f588e:

#   l "Yes, I'll be there."
    l "Sí, allí estaré."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:405
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_4b5a0763:

#   l "Hey!"
    l "¡Eh!"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:408
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_a1b439cc:

#   l "I am!"
    l "¡Lo estoy!"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:410
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_26639176:

#   l "We all thought we’d lost you!"
    l "¡Todos pensábamos que te habíamos perdido!"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:411
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_05ea1d86:

#   l "It was such a relief when we found you with that locator."
    l "Fue un gran alivio cuando te encontramos con ese localizador."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:412
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_f2063490:

#   c "I’m very glad you went to those lengths to find me."
    c "Me alegro mucho de que hicieras todo lo posible por encontrarme."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:414
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_478ecc95:

#   l "Did your father really push you out an airlock?"
    l "¿De verdad tu padre te empujó por una esclusa de aire?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:415
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_b25f5846:

#   c "Something like that, yeah."
    c "Algo así, sí."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:417
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_dc0b7a97:

#   l "That’s so awful."
    l "Eso es horrible."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:418
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_b036f3fd:

#   c "Well, he needed a sacrifice and I was just lucky enough to be around."
    c "Bueno, necesitaba un sacrificio y yo tuve la suerte de estar cerca."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:419
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_43182e1c:

#   l "You shouldn’t joke about those things."
    l "No deberías bromear con esas cosas."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:420
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_ecc1126f:

#   c "I don’t know how else to deal with it."
    c "No sé de qué otra forma afrontarlo."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:421
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_eb407b1b:

#   l "Yeah, I can imagine."
    l "Sí, me lo imagino."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:422
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_fa65b030:

#   l "It's a very cold thing to do though."
    l "Sin embargo, es algo muy frío."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:423
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_7a9a4e48:

#   c "It sure is, but I've come to expect this from my parents."
    c "Seguro que lo es, pero he llegado a esperar esto de mis padres."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:425
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_9f78720c:

#   l "Not outright murder, surely."
    l "No un asesinato descarado, seguramente."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:426
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_142aeaf5:

#   c "I admit that's a new thing, but not very surprising really."
    c "Admito que es algo nuevo, pero no muy sorprendente en realidad."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:428
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_bd1a32e8:

#   l "Still, it makes me very sad."
    l "Aun así, me entristece mucho."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:430
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_05c28db0:

#   l "Very happy to see you’re safe and sound though."
    l "Me alegra ver que estás sano y salvo."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:431
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_c6ce0e47:

#   c "Thanks Lilly."
    c "Gracias Lilly."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:432
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_1173e89a:

#   l "The others will surely want to see you."
    l "Seguro que los demás querrán verte."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:433
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_09ac0171:

#   c "I’ve spoken to a few of them already."
    c "Ya he hablado con algunos de ellos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:434
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_670b93fb:

#   l "Take care, [p_name_short]."
    l "Cuídate, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:341
translate spanish ep013_lilly_talk_2fc60e3f_1:

#   "I left Lilly in a state of utter confusion, hoping it would all turn out for the best."
    "Dejé a Lilly en un estado de confusión absoluta, con la esperanza de que todo saliera bien."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:344
