    na "Fueron las esporas..."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:779
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_63e6cc41:

#   c "If that's still the excuse you want to hide behind, I'm not stopping you."
    c "Si esa sigue siendo la excusa tras la que quieres esconderte, no te lo impediré."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:780
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_706d6e73:

#   c "I just want you to know that my feelings for you haven't changed, your revelations notwithstanding."
    c "Sólo quiero que sepas que mis sentimientos por ti no han cambiado, a pesar de tus revelaciones."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:781
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_d57fb92b:

#   c "I love you unconditionally and even more so now that I know you're my mother."
    c "Te quiero incondicionalmente y más ahora que sé que eres mi madre."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:782
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_b443c32e:

#   c "Please allow yourself some time to consider and I'll be waiting for your answer."
    c "Por favor, tómese un tiempo para reflexionar y espero su respuesta."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:784
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_abc4ae49:

#   na "[p_name]...{w} I....{w} Thank you, I will."
    na "[p_name]...{w} I....{w} Gracias, lo haré."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:786
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_380ce082:

#   c "One thing I want you to know beforehand is that I'm very happy you've told me the truth."
    c "Una cosa que quiero que sepas de antemano es que estoy muy contento de que me hayas dicho la verdad."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:787
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_3150f0bb:

#   c "It has taken quite a lot of time, but I know and respect how difficult the decision was for you."
    c "Me ha llevado bastante tiempo, pero sé y respeto lo difícil que ha sido la decisión para ti."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:788
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_5752ef6b:

#   c "So if you'll permit me, I would very much like to call you mother."
    c "Así que si me lo permites, me gustaría mucho llamarte madre."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:790
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_b02f6586:

#   na "Of course, that would mean the world to me!"
    na "Por supuesto, ¡eso significaría mucho para mí!"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:792
translate spanish ep013_nadya_talk_c39ef11c:

#   "Nadya took me in a loving embrace, the burden of years of secrecy suddenly lifted."
    "Nadya me estrechó en un abrazo cariñoso, la carga de años de secretismo se disipó de repente."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:798
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_8e87aab4:

#   ra "You must have heard it a thousand times already, but I’m so glad you’re okay."
    ra "Ya lo habrás oído mil veces, pero me alegro mucho de que estés bien."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:799
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_791eb68c:

#   c "Merely glad?"
    c "¿Simplemente contento?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:801
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_bcdcf469:

#   "I pulled her towards me and kissed Raene."
    "La atraje hacia mí y besé a Raene."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:802
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_482e386e:

#   "When we disentangled, her words were a breathless whisper."
    "Cuando nos desenredamos, sus palabras eran un susurro sin aliento."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:804
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_86de2e99:

#   ra "I missed you so much."
    ra "Te he echado mucho de menos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:806
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_51d9764c:

#   "We kissed again and Raene held me tightly, as if she didn’t want to let go of me anymore."
    "Volvimos a besarnos y Raene me abrazó con fuerza, como si ya no quisiera soltarme."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:809
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_a88c61e8:

#   "The hunger behind our kisses surprised us both and Raene gasped as our tongues collided."
    "El hambre que había detrás de nuestros besos nos sorprendió a los dos y Raene jadeó cuando nuestras lenguas chocaron."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:811
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_170df0b3:

#   "As we exchanged a passionate french kiss, I covered the curve of one of her small breasts with my hand."
    "Mientras intercambiábamos un apasionado beso francés, cubrí con mi mano la curva de uno de sus pequeños pechos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:812
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_02a41a45:

#   ra "Oh [p_name_short]!"
    ra "Oh [p_name_short]!"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:814
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_c30bc9d4:

#   "Hypnotized, I pressed my body closer against hers."
    "Hipnotizada, apreté más mi cuerpo contra el suyo."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:815
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_5a04a09f:

#   "I was about to push her gently onto her bed, when I felt the swell of her growing erection against my thigh."
    "Estaba a punto de empujarla suavemente sobre su cama, cuando sentí el oleaje de su creciente erección contra mi muslo."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:817
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_d8316ca8:

#   "As soon as Raene also became aware of the sensation, her eyes darted open and she pulled away from me quickly."
    "En cuanto Raene se percató de la sensación, abrió los ojos y se apartó de mí rápidamente."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:819
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_7ef3b148:

#   "Mumbling something apologetic, she tore away from me and ran out of her quarters."
    "Murmurando algo de disculpa, se separó de mí y salió corriendo de sus aposentos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:820
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_8e306f26:

#   c "Raene?!"
    c "¡¿Raene?!"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:822
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_d408546f:

#   "I waited in her room for a long while, but Raene didn’t return."
    "Esperé en su habitación un buen rato, pero Raene no volvió."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:823
translate spanish ep013_raene_talk_863286ae:

#   "Vowing to speak to her later, I left her quarters."
    "Prometiendo hablar con ella más tarde, salí de sus aposentos."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:831
translate spanish ep013_raene_second_talk_787b4719:

#   c "Hey you."
    c "Hola."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:832
translate spanish ep013_raene_second_talk_6d9915ab:

#   ra "Hey."
    ra "Hola."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:833
translate spanish ep013_raene_second_talk_59e8f5b7:

#   c "Are you okay to talk?"
    c "¿Estás bien para hablar?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:835
translate spanish ep013_raene_second_talk_8fc48ebc:

#   ra "Yes, about earlier...{w} [p_name_short]...{w} I’m sorry..."
    ra "Sí, sobre antes...{w} [p_name_short]...{w} Lo siento..."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:836
translate spanish ep013_raene_second_talk_9cf34866:

#   c "No need to apologize, but I’d like to talk to you about it nevertheless."
    c "No hace falta que te disculpes, pero aun así me gustaría hablar contigo de ello."

