#   ce "What happened?"
    ce "¿Qué ha pasado?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:891
translate spanish ep013_celine_talk_f2f16b6b:

#   c "I've found someone else, that's all I can say."
    c "He encontrado a alguien más, es todo lo que puedo decir."

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:893
translate spanish ep013_celine_talk_8fc38651:

#   ce "And she's making you do this?"
    ce "¿Y te obliga a hacer esto?"

# game/episode013_conversations.rpy:894
translate spanish ep013_celine_talk_6ec5eda3:

#   ce "What we had was true, [p_name_short], and you're throwing it all away."
    ce "Lo que teníamos era verdad, [p_name_short], y lo estás tirando todo por la borda."

